description: And what a hit she is! As usual of course. There is alot of joy involved in shooting someone over and over again who actually comes through over and over again. Wenona is, as most of you know by now, dependable, consistantly tough, her attitude is always good and lets not forget that incredible body that she keeps in such good shape for us! Thanks again Wenona for a job well done!
title: Wenona strikes again!
